-story/36e11c8db4052604a7bc02c96842b356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailytelegraph.com.au%2Frendezview%2Fpresumption-of-innocence-shouldnt-mean-silencing-survivors%2Fnews-story%2F36e11c8db4052604a7bc02c96842b356&d=yokb69uU2TaPlFT3jV6eC%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=3f21e3a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/rendezview/presumption-of-innocence-shouldnt-mean-silencing-survivors/news-story/36e11c8db4052604a7bc02c96842b356</a> (鬼都洗左腦, 相反 D comment 重清醒過佢)<br />\n<br />\nWhat we should NOT do is start a mob to punish the accused, regardless of whether they are guilty or not. That is for the justice system to decide. Because if we tarnish on the basis of accusation alone, and if we ruin a single person's life as a result, then we as people have failed. <br />\n<br />\nJustice is for the justice system. Support is for the victim. Process is for the accused.<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭工黨重諗住將責任推落被告到, 你話痴唔痴撚綫"},{"pid":"b45604da5e27dcb7ab67da6072126c0190d67dbc","tid":498554,"uid":31151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:55:14.000Z","msg":"破你膠處(笑)"},{"pid":"abde031b74866ec81035c8ca6d427d50ed663a7d","tid":498554,"uid":100283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:10:47.000Z","msg":"黃蓉邊有係洪七公度學廚呀，金庸唯一寫過洪七公煮野食好似得神雕入面炸蜈蚣，射雕入面佢淨係負責食咋嘛"},{"pid":"4a2c49cd001e50fea5082ff978520821b0f56c26","tid":498554,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d49ba5cf538eac588d54ec01517bd645b22d131","tid":498554,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃蓉邊有係洪七公度學廚呀，金庸唯一寫過洪七公煮野食好似得神雕入面炸蜈蚣，射雕入面佢淨係負責食咋嘛</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 